channel.title: Webclient error - What does it mean?
channel.description:
Hey guys, well i'm somehow getting a webclient error, when I run my webclient it says (in the cmd file) 'Error: Startup error 20' What does that mean?
P.s this only happens when I load the cache from the C drive, so if you know how to make the cache download to the desktop that would be wonderful!
Thanks, ProjectDiabolus
